{"tid":318710,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(純發洩)覺得好似俾人用黎攝時間咁，尊重何在？","createTime":"2017-07-12T09:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T15:48:22.000Z","uid":128016,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70c80b91e71a223f1d29456ca44e9efb43eb8720","tid":318710,"uid":128016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:33:28.000Z","msg":"有事鍾無艷，無事夏迎春<br />\n<br />\n永遠你搵親我就秒回，我搵親你就十問九唔應，十句先覆一句，十個字先覆一兩個字，一係就索性已讀不回。<br />\n即使幾忙都好，事後覆返人是基本禮貌吧？全世界唔係淨係得你一個忙，得你有人約，唔係個個都事必要24小時standby俾晒你黎攝時間。<br />\n得唔得都係一句，約親你都答未知/唔知係咩意思？後備呀？攝時間呀？<br />\n人與人之間既相處貴乎互相尊重。<br />\n你不知不覺間已經多次觸及我既底線而不自知，問心，我唔相信你對其他人會係咁，普通朋友都唔會係咁，呢樣就係我最介意既地方。<br />\n<br />\n我不過是個人 都會難堪"},{"pid":"205840fbd1275211798a5fa9c64fba3a262ec607","tid":318710,"uid":84012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"兵仔埋嚟攞更表啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d3f36cbc3d9d6e081b56a5363cdaa264dd0517","tid":318710,"uid":15174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"我仲以為係自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952ff729b3e2c7b7913177dbdaff7610a9fdae0a","tid":318710,"uid":128016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:43:42.000Z","msg":"兩位巴打，但我係絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4660ed7e98bca466f9abdc901f5c1e9e9b9c8e2e","tid":318710,"uid":112249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"你一定要搵佢既～！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試下唔搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1acedfc289f6db6e7a4609953cf312a